==English==
===Noun===
'''[[carbon]] [[dioxide]]''' {{uncountable}}
{{wikipedia}}
#{{chemistry}} The normal [[oxide]] of [[carbon]], CO<sub>2</sub>; a [[colourless]], [[odourless]] [[gas]] formed during [[respiration]] and [[combustion]] and [[consumed]] by [[plant]]s during [[photosynthesis]].

